## Template Patterns

### Entry Queries
```twig
{% set entries = craft.entries()
    .section('blog')
    .orderBy('postDate desc')
    .limit(10)
    .all() %}

{% for entry in entries %}
    <h2>{{ entry.title }}</h2>
{% endfor %}
```

### Assets
```twig
{% set image = entry.featuredImage.one() %}
{% if image %}
    <img src="{{ image.url }}" alt="{{ image.alt }}">
{% endif %}
```

